desc:
For our Boston office, we are looking for a Senior JavaScript (React) Engineer that can successfully transform the dream design of our clients into a well-functioning platform.

As a Senior JavaScript Engineer, you will work on a variety of global digital projects for high profile B2B and B2C brands. You will build mobile-first, cross-browser compatible, high performing websites and strive to look for better tools and techniques to introduce into the workplace. You will ensure the client Technical Wiki’s are kept up to date and you will continuously strive to improve your craft.

You will be responsible for driving JavaScript technologies within our development team, ensuring we're using the right tools and technologies at the right time.

You will work in a vibrant environment with clever minds that work for a variety of large global clients. Yes, we are eager to hire the most talented experts in the game but we are also looking for a perfect Dept-fit. Someone who is eager to learn, inspires, strives towards a better world, takes the stage, a futurist at heart, and someone who will toast to a successful week with us.

YOU:
Are an expert in front-end technologies including ES6+, React JS, Redux/Redux Saga;

Have experience in testing methodologies and supporting frameworks e.g. Jest/TDD;

Have experience in REST API Integrations;

Have an extreme attention for detail and strive for perfection;

Have experience or awareness of build tools (e.g. Gulp and webpack) and using source control (Git);

Are able to translate creative ideas and mockups into interactive prototypes;

Ideally have experience of building for a CMS;

Have some awareness of TypeScript and nodejs;

Are one of those ambitious people who can switch from serious to play in a heartbeat.

WE OFFER:
An open culture;

Develop yourself at one of the fastest growing digital agencies in Europe, from our beautiful office in Boston;

Possibilities to do what you do best and to develop your skills even further;

Healthy and tasty food;

Bootcamp trainings;

Friday drinks/open bar;

Legendary team outings;

An excellent salary based on experience;

Great fringe benefits: think laptop, mobile, travel expenses and all that stuff.

WHO ARE WE?

Hi, we are Dept - an international digital agency of over a 1,000 experienced thinkers & makers. One agency uniting creativity, technology and data. Helping reinvent & accelerate your digital reality by creating experiences that people want and businesses need.

An assessment can be part of the application procedure.
